                "post_type": "page",
                "content_format": "blocks",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us for a relaxed afternoon in the neighborhood with grilled favorites, cold drinks, and lawn games for all ages. Bring a side dish to share if you'd like, and don't forget a chair \u2014 we'll set up under the shade trees by the cul-de-sac.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Confirm the headcount and assign side dishes one week ahead.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pick up burgers, buns, charcoal, and drinks the day before.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Set up tables, the grill, and lawn games the morning of the cookout.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#menu\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->"
            }
        }
